OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sat 28 Feb to Mon 9 Mar
OL,6,FChangeable conditions are expected,
OL,7,Fwith Atlantic frontal systems
OL,8,Fspreading across the UK, interspersed
OL,9,Fwith drier and brighter interludes.
OL,10,FRainfall will typically be heaviest in
OL,11,Fthe northwest, with much less reaching
OL,12,Fsheltered eastern areas. Some snow is
OL,13,Fpossible across high ground in the
OL,14,Fnorth. Drier and more settled periods
OL,15,Fperhaps become more prolonged later in
OL,16,Fthe period, especially in the east.
OL,17,FWinds will probably be strong at
OL,18,Ftimes, with a risk of gales.
OL,19,FTemperatures are likely to be near to
OL,20,For slightly above average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
