OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tue 10 Mar to Tue 24 Mar
OL,6,FChangeable conditions will probably
OL,7,Fdominate during this period, with
OL,8,FAtlantic frontal systems spreading
OL,9,Facross the UK. These will bring spells
OL,10,Fof rain and perhaps strong winds, with
OL,11,Fthe wettest conditions in the
OL,12,Fnorthwest. The southeast will likely
OL,13,Fbe driest, perhaps with some longer
OL,14,Fspells of dry weather developing for
OL,15,Fthe south later. Temperatures are
OL,16,Flikely to be near to or slightly above
OL,17,Fnormal overall.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
